scenes.description: Mori Calliope jokingly 'steps' on the miniature 3D models of her fellow Hololive Myth members.
MC section where Mori thanks the Myth girls for joining her and sends them off.
Mori takes a water break and introduces her next special guests.
Performance of the song 'Graveyard Shift' featuring Boogey Voxx.
